1 NOTE {geni:about_me} Vladimir V. Koudacheff was first married to Baronnesse Fanni Adele Koudacheff  in 1913 and divorced from her. after the Revolution. She died in 1929. He was in the corps de page and took part in the Fist World War,
2 CONC  where he was wounded. He was an excellent horsemen and fencing champion. 
2 CONT
2 CONT After he settled in the USA and married Lucy Marsh Leggett, he engaged in food production with Whole Foods
