1 NOTE {geni:about_me} ==Biography==
2 CONT '''Leonid Vladimirovitch HORVATH''' was born in 1880. His father was [https://www.geni.com/profile-34639129983 Vladimir Leonidovitch HORVATH]. 
2 CONT
2 CONT Leonid married [https://www.geni.com/profile-34753378133 Olga Nikolaevna HORVATH (Krasnov)]. Together they had the following children: [https://www.geni.com/profile-34753388564 Vladimir Leonidovich HORVATH]. 
2 CONT ----
2 CONT Paternal haplogroup I-M438, I-S17250.  Origin and Migrations of Haplogroups I-M438   The men of haplogroup I-M438 radiated outward from the Balkans into the eastern half of the continent. Their descendants are found most concentra
2 CONC ted in eastern Europe and western Russia, where they make up 40% of the male population in Bosnia and 30% in Croatia. Some, however, moved farther north and west. Nearly 40% of men on the Mediterranean island of Sardinia carry hap
2 CONC logroup I-M438, and they are also relatively common in the Netherlands and Germany. Finally, they can also be found in Sweden, particularly in the northern province of Vasterbotten, where their ancestors likely arrived with the mo
2 CONC re recent migration of German and Dutch immigrants during the 17th century.
