2 CONT '''Olga Nikolaevna HORVATH (Krasnov)''' was born in 1888. Her parents were [https://www.geni.com/profile-34753383728 Nikolai KRASNOV] and [https://www.geni.com/profile-34753388985 Anna Mikhailovna KRASNOV (Farbstein)]. 
