2 CONC artCopy/18783 SmartCopy]: ''Aug 28 2015, 15:10:52 UTC''
2 CONT
2 CONT Namesake in 1908 for Hathaway House, a dormitory at Milton Academy that represented a significant expansion of the girls school. (source: Milton Academy, 1798-1948, Richard W. Hale)
