1 NOTE {geni:about_me} Mary Watson (1813-1890)
2 CONT
2 CONT Mary was born on 20 January 1813 to Stephen Hathaway and Lydia Swain. She was married on 1 July 1833 to Robert Sedgwick Watson, the son of Ebenezer Watson and Frances Sedgwick. Her maiden name was Mary Taber Hathaway and she had a
2 CONC  twin, Sarah Swain Hathaway who was married to John Murray Forbes. She died in Milton on 20 December 1890.
