1 NOTE {geni:about_me}  Hannah Nye was the sister of Sylvia Hathaway Nye Swift and Thomas S. H.  Nye.  She never married. Her gravestone shows this.  In her later years she lived with her sister Sylvia  and brother- in- law Rhodolphus Ny
2 CONC e Swift.  After their deaths she lived with her nephew, the artist Clement Nye Swift ,and his wife Annie Amelie Nye Swift on the Nye farm in Achusnet.  
2 CONT          Annie Amelie Nye was the only child of Sylvias brother  Thomas S. H.  Nye and Annie Deblois, so Annie Amelie's  husband Clement was her first cousin. He was 49 at the time of the marriage in 1895.
2 CONT    The History of Achshnut ,written by Franklyn Howland  and published in 1907 shows that Sylvia H. Nye was not married. The 1900 census showing her as married and a mother is incorrect.
2 CONT   .
