1 NOTE {geni:about_me} * http://et.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arved_von_Taube
2 CONT * http://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arved_von_Taube
2 CONT *[http://www.ra.ee/dgs/_purl.php?shc=TLA.237.2.15:336 Sünd vkj 14. oktoobril 1905. TLA.237.2.15:336]
2 CONT *[http://www.ra.ee/apps/andmed/index.php/matrikkel/view?id=6835 ''Album Academicum Universitatis Tartuensis 1918-1944'']
2 CONT *[http://www.ra.ee/fotis/index.php?type=2&id=733358Historian & writer. Member of stud. corp! "Estonia"]
2 CONT *He  studied History and Political Science at Tartu University under Arno Rafael Cederberg . After graduation in 1931 on "Dorpat under Swedish rule in the years 1601-1603" Taube continued his studies for three semesters in Leipzig
2 CONC  and Berlin.
2 CONT *Foto - http://www.ra.ee/fotis/index.php/et/photo/view?id=48390&_xr=5d37385aab60d
2 CONT *He & his family resettled to Germany during World War II, ending his days in the vicinity of Bremen
2 CONT *Arved von Taube drowned in a sailing accident off the southern coast of Portugal.
